CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Industrial Logistics Properties Trust is a real estate investment trust. It owns and leases industrial and logistics properties throughout the United States. The company's investment portfolio includes industrial lands in Hawaii and industrial and logistics properties in other states. Rental revenue is earned from Hawaii Properties and Mainland Properties.
